T1  - A Study of Optimality in Recurrent Decision-Making of Lower-Level Managers
AU  - Shrode, William A.
AU  - Brown, Warren B.
Y1  - 1970/12/01
PY  - 1970
DA  - 1970/12/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/254829
